00:00:12,013 --> 00:00:14,913
We should only be
gone a day. Two max.

5
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:18,295
If you need me before
then, you can just...

6
00:00:18,319 --> 00:00:19,451
Please...

7
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,082
Harriet's dying for some
quality time with her grand mom.

8
00:00:22,106 --> 00:00:23,850
I could've just
taken her with me.

9
00:00:26,243 --> 00:00:27,963
<i>You can prepare all you want.</i>

10
00:00:29,096 --> 00:00:31,141
Aren't you gonna
say, like, "Go, child,

